#originalTopic=It_Would_Be_Much_Safer_If_Everyone_Carried_A_Gun
 I'm British. Our halfwits find it reasonably difficult to get their hands on a gun. Ours carry knives.   /> By the same reasoning, all should carry knives, whether we go to the pub or shopping, we should all be tooled up. Your granny should take a machette to the womens guild. Just in case...  /> If all were to carry a gun, every Saturday night would be the gun fight at the OK coral.